# Lariat Car Rental — Revenue Analysis & Strategic Scenarios
**Tools:** Microsoft Excel (Advanced)

---

## Overview

This project analyzes car rental business performance for Lariat across locations, inventory mix, and revenue trends. Using Advanced Excel, three strategic scenarios were developed for 2019 revenue improvement — each with supporting projections, calculations, and full formula transparency preserved throughout.

---

## View the Project

> **Note:** The Excel workbook is too large to preview directly in GitHub.  
> **[Click here to open the full workbook](https://tinyurl.com/Lariat-Excel-Cosby)**

---

## What's Inside

The workbook contains multiple sheets covering:

- **Source data** — raw car rental performance data across locations and inventory
- **Inventory growth scenario** — projected revenue increase of $65,734
- **Location performance reallocation scenario** — analysis of underperforming vs. high-performing locations
- **Inventory reinvestment scenario** — projected revenue increase of $96,445
- **Supporting calculations** — all formulas visible and intact for full transparency

---

## Analytical Question

Which strategic levers — inventory growth, location reallocation, or reinvestment — offer the strongest path to revenue improvement, and by how much?

---

